headline.main: 11 PARACHUTISTS SHOT BY FRENCH IN ALGERIA; Condemned by Court-Martial With Two Arab Aides

lead_paragraph: ALLIED HEADQUARTERS IN NORTH AFRICA, Feb. 1 -- Eleven parachutists dropped behind the Allied lines in civilian clothes were shot as spies at Biskra, Algeria, on Saturday, after having been condemned to death by a French court-martial.
abstract: 11 parachutists and 2 Arab aides executed by French on espionage charges, Algeria
